00072 UINT8 RemoveFirstAIListEntry( void )
00073 {
00074       AILIST *    pOldFirstEntry;
00075       UINT8             ubID;
00076 
00077       while ( gpFirstAIListEntry != NULL)
00078       {
00079             // record pointer to start of list, and advance head ptr
00080             pOldFirstEntry = gpFirstAIListEntry;
00081             gpFirstAIListEntry = gpFirstAIListEntry->pNext;
00082 
00083             // record ID, and delete old now unused entry
00084             ubID = pOldFirstEntry->ubID;
00085             DeleteAIListEntry( pOldFirstEntry );
00086 
00087             // make sure conditions still met
00088             if ( SatisfiesAIListConditions( MercPtrs[ ubID ], NULL, FALSE ) )
00089             {
00090                   return( ubID );
00091             }
00092       }
00093 
00094       return( NOBODY );
00095 }

00097 void RemoveAIListEntryForID( UINT8 ubID )
00098 {
00099       AILIST *    pEntry;
00100       AILIST *    pPrevEntry;
00101 
00102       pEntry = gpFirstAIListEntry;
00103       pPrevEntry = NULL;

00105       while( pEntry != NULL )
00106       {
00107             if ( pEntry->ubID == ubID )

00110                   {
00111                         RemoveFirstAIListEntry();
00112                   }
00113                   else
00114                   {
00115                         pPrevEntry->pNext = pEntry->pNext;
00116                         DeleteAIListEntry( pEntry );
00117                   }
00118                   return;
00119             }
00120             pPrevEntry = pEntry;
00121             pEntry = pEntry->pNext;
00122       }
00123       // none found, that's okay

00126 BOOLEAN InsertIntoAIList( UINT8 ubID, INT8 bPriority )
00127 {
00128       UINT8             ubNewEntry;
00129       AILIST *    pEntry, * pNewEntry, * pPrevEntry = NULL;
00130 
00131       ubNewEntry = FindEmptyAIListEntry();
00132             
00133       pNewEntry = CreateNewAIListEntry( ubNewEntry, ubID, bPriority );
00134 
00135       // look through the list now to see where to insert the entry
00136       if (gpFirstAIListEntry == NULL)
00137       {
00138             // empty list!
00139             gpFirstAIListEntry = pNewEntry;
00140             // new entry's next ptr is null already
00141             return( TRUE );
00142       }
00143       else
00144       {
00145             pEntry = gpFirstAIListEntry;
00146             do 
00147             {
00148                   if ( bPriority > pEntry->bPriority )
00149                   {
00150                         // insert before this entry
00151                         pNewEntry->pNext = pEntry;
00152                         if (pEntry == gpFirstAIListEntry)
00153                         {
00154                               // inserting at head of list
00155                               gpFirstAIListEntry = pNewEntry;
00156                         }
00157                         else
00158                         {
00159                               Assert(pPrevEntry != NULL);
00160                               pPrevEntry->pNext = pNewEntry;
00161                         }
00162                         return( TRUE );
00163                   }
00164                   else if (pEntry->pNext == NULL)
00165                   {
00166                         // end of list!
00167                         pEntry->pNext = pNewEntry;
00168                         return( TRUE );
00169                   }
00170                   pPrevEntry = pEntry;
00171                   pEntry = pEntry->pNext;
00172                   AssertMsg( pEntry != gpFirstAIListEntry, "Fatal error: Loop in AI list!" );
00173             }
00174             while( pEntry != NULL );
00175       }
00176 
00177       // I don't know how the heck we would get here...
00178       return( FALSE );
00179 }

00181 BOOLEAN SatisfiesAIListConditions( SOLDIERTYPE * pSoldier, UINT8 * pubDoneCount, BOOLEAN fDoRandomChecks ) 
00182 {
00183       if ( (gTacticalStatus.bBoxingState == BOXING) && !(pSoldier->uiStatusFlags & SOLDIER_BOXER) )
00184       {
00185             return( FALSE );
00186       }
00187 
00188       if ( ! ( pSoldier->bActive && pSoldier->bInSector ) ) 
00189       {
00190             // the check for 
00191             return( FALSE );
00192       }
00193 
00194       if ( ! ( pSoldier->bLife >= OKLIFE && pSoldier->bBreath >= OKBREATH ) )
00195       {
00196             return( FALSE );
00197       }
00198 
00199       if ( pSoldier->bMoved )
00200       {
00201             if ( pSoldier->bActionPoints <= 1 && pubDoneCount )
00202             {
00203                   (*pubDoneCount)++;
00204             }
00205             return( FALSE );
00206       }
00207 
00208       // do we need to re-evaluate alert status here?
00209       DecideAlertStatus( pSoldier );
00210 
00211       // if we are dealing with the civ team and this person
00212       // hasn't heard any gunfire, handle only 1 time in 10
00213       if (PTR_CIVILIAN)
00214       {
00215             if ( pSoldier->ubBodyType == CROW || pSoldier->ubBodyType == COW )
00216             {
00217                   // don't handle cows and crows in TB!
00218                   return( FALSE );
00219             }
00220 
00221             // if someone in a civ group is neutral but the civ group is non-neutral, should be handled all the time
00222             if ( pSoldier->bNeutral && (pSoldier->ubCivilianGroup == NON_CIV_GROUP || gTacticalStatus.fCivGroupHostile[pSoldier->ubCivilianGroup] == CIV_GROUP_NEUTRAL ) )
00223             {
00224                   if ( pSoldier->bAlertStatus < STATUS_RED )
00225                   {
00226                         // unalerted, barely handle
00227                         if ( fDoRandomChecks && PreRandom( 10 ) && !(pSoldier->ubQuoteRecord) )
00228                         {
00229                               return( FALSE );
00230                         }
00231                   }
00232                   else
00233                   {
00234                         // heard gunshots
00235                         if ( pSoldier->uiStatusFlags & SOLDIER_COWERING ) 
00236                         {
00237                               if ( pSoldier->bVisible )
00238                               {
00239                                     // if have profile, don't handle, don't want them running around
00240                                     if ( pSoldier->ubProfile != NO_PROFILE )
00241                                     {
00242                                           return( FALSE );
00243                                     }
00244                                     // else don't handle much
00245                                     if ( fDoRandomChecks && PreRandom( 3 ) )
00246                                     {
00247                                           return( FALSE );
00248                                     }
00249                               }
00250                               else
00251                               {
00252                                     // never handle
00253                                     return( FALSE );
00254                               }
00255                         }
00256                         else if ( pSoldier->ubBodyType == COW || pSoldier->ubBodyType == CRIPPLECIV )
00257                         {
00258                               // don't handle much
00259                               if ( fDoRandomChecks && PreRandom( 3 ) )
00260                               {
00261                                     return( FALSE );
00262                               }
00263                         }
00264                   }
00265             }
00266             // non-neutral civs should be handled all the time, right?
00267             // reset last action if cowering
00268 
00269             if ( pSoldier->uiStatusFlags & SOLDIER_COWERING ) 
00270             {
00271                   pSoldier->bLastAction = AI_ACTION_NONE;
00272             }
00273 
00274       }
00275 
00276       return( TRUE );
00277 }

00279 BOOLEAN MoveToFrontOfAIList( UINT8 ubID )
00280 {
00281       // we'll have to fake this guy's alert status (in the list) to be the same as the current
00282       // front of the list
00283       INT8              bPriority;
00284       UINT8             ubNewEntry;
00285       AILIST *    pNewEntry;
00286 
00287       if ( !SatisfiesAIListConditions( MercPtrs[ ubID ], NULL, FALSE ) )
00288       {
00289             // can't do dat!
00290             return( FALSE );
00291       }
00292 
00293       RemoveAIListEntryForID( ubID );
00294 
00295       if (gpFirstAIListEntry == NULL)
00296       {
00297             return( InsertIntoAIList( ubID, MAX_AI_PRIORITY ) ); 
00298       }
00299       else
00300       {
00301             bPriority = gpFirstAIListEntry->bPriority;
00302             ubNewEntry = FindEmptyAIListEntry();      
00303             pNewEntry = CreateNewAIListEntry( ubNewEntry, ubID, bPriority );
00304 
00305             // insert at front
00306             pNewEntry->pNext = gpFirstAIListEntry;
00307             gpFirstAIListEntry = pNewEntry;
00308             return( TRUE );
00309       }
00310 }

00312 BOOLEAN BuildAIListForTeam( INT8 bTeam )
00313 {
00314       // loop through all non-player-team guys and add to list
00315       UINT32                              uiLoop;
00316       BOOLEAN                             fInsertRet;
00317       SOLDIERTYPE *           pSoldier;
00318       BOOLEAN                             fRet = FALSE;
00319       UINT8                               ubCount = 0;
00320       UINT8                               ubDoneCount = 0;
00321       INT8                                bPriority;
00322 
00323       // this team is being given control so reset their muzzle flashes
00324       TurnOffTeamsMuzzleFlashes( bTeam );
00325 
00326       // clear the AI list
00327       ClearAIList();
00328             
00329       // create a new list
00330       for( uiLoop = 0; uiLoop < guiNumMercSlots; uiLoop++ )
00331       {
00332             // non-null merc slot ensures active 
00333             pSoldier = MercSlots[ uiLoop ];
00334             if ( pSoldier && pSoldier->bTeam == bTeam )
00335             {
00336                   if ( !SatisfiesAIListConditions( pSoldier, &ubDoneCount, TRUE ) )
00337                   {
00338                         continue;
00339                   }
00340 
00341                   bPriority = pSoldier->bAlertStatus;
00342                   if ( pSoldier->bVisible == TRUE )
00343                   {
00344                         bPriority += 3;
00345                   }
00346 
00347                   fInsertRet = InsertIntoAIList( pSoldier->ubID, bPriority );
00348                   if (fInsertRet == FALSE)
00349                   {
00350                         // wtf???
00351                         break;
00352                   }
00353                   else
00354                   {
00355                         fRet = TRUE;
00356                         ubCount++;
00357                   }
00358             }
00359       }
00360 
00361       if (fRet && ubCount > 0)
00362       {
00363             InitEnemyUIBar( ubCount, ubDoneCount );
00364       }
00365       return( fRet );
00366 }
